00:07:30.350 --> 00:07:36.320
So it kind of, I kind of feel like I can't
miss, I might not be everyone's favorite,

00:07:36.320 --> 00:07:43.449
but if I am true than whether it is film,
TV, theatre or concert it doesn't really matter.

00:07:43.449 --> 00:07:46.230
