00:26:46.879 --> 00:26:48.450
&gt;&gt; Kristin: It's so crazy when I think about
it.

00:26:48.450 --> 00:26:53.590
I like to be able to say, first I thought,
I don't understand the concept of Twitter.

00:26:53.590 --> 00:26:55.479
Ashton; "Are you kidding me.

