me like to hear from me I like to hear from

00:27:14.710 --> 00:27:15.710
them.

00:27:15.710 --> 00:27:19.730
Like, the other day, this women was like "I
bite my tongue and who knew that the next

00:27:19.730 --> 00:27:22.330
day a chunk would be missing and it hurt so
bad!"

00:27:22.330 --> 00:27:26.020
