00:27:26.020 --> 00:27:29.749
I like to hear [ laughs ] I like to hear just
regular, cause I am pretty much down to earth.

00:27:29.749 --> 00:27:32.499
It's kind of what you see is what you get.

00:27:32.499 --> 00:27:35.570
So, um, anyway, that's why I love it, I love
it!

00:27:35.570 --> 00:27:37.719
&gt;&gt; Lee: Have you ever considered using Google
plus?

00:27:37.719 --> 00:27:39.950
[ laughter ]
It's kind of like Twitter.

00:27:39.950 --> 00:27:42.940
&gt;&gt; Kristin: Well when you ask me like that.

