radio show today and she was saying that that

00:31:00.649 --> 00:31:03.710
was a very special moment because it forced
Oprah.

00:31:03.710 --> 00:31:08.469
Who's not always, we may always see her giving
but receiving is hard for her.

00:31:08.469 --> 00:31:15.359
So she had to receive that and so I was so
glad she was able to let loose and see what

00:31:15.359 --> 00:31:18.349
she had done, put all these men through college.

00:31:18.349 --> 00:31:20.129
I mean, "what?"

00:31:20.129 --> 00:31:23.259
Talk about making your mark on this world.

00:31:23.259 --> 00:31:25.159
She is great.

00:31:25.159 --> 00:31:26.419
Thank you.

